post_summaries.description: The image shows a natural straw rabbit nest from rabbitsupplystore. The nest is made of woven straw and has a small entrance. To the left of the nest is a wooden ramp with dowel rungs, and below is a circular scratching pad. The entire setup is placed on artificial turf.

The image shows two rabbits on a straw mat inside a blue wire cage. There are also two additional straw mats shown below. The post is from rabbitsupplystore promoting the straw mat as a way to entertain rabbits.

The image is an advertisement for rabbit harnesses from rabbitsupplystore. It features several rabbits, a hamster, and different styles of harnesses. The harnesses are designed to be used with a leash for walking rabbits.
The image shows a grey rabbit surrounded by four different types of woven balls, presumably toys for rabbits. The Instagram post promotes these "boredom busters" made from natural materials.
